---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import SiteHeader from '../components/SiteHeader.astro';
---


<Layout
  title="Articles | Fastlane Synthetics"
  description="Helpful AMSOIL articles, product guidance, and maintenance information from Fastlane Synthetics."
>
  <main class="min-h-screen bg-white text-slate-900">
    <SiteHeader currentPath="/articles" />

    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
      <img
        src="/amsoilbackgroundarticles.png"
        alt="AMSOIL articles background"
        class="absolute inset-0 h-full w-full object-cover object-[center_55%] opacity-75"
      />
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/35"></div>

      <div class="relative z-10 mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 md:px-10 md:py-20">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">

          <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-black leading-tight text-white md:text-6xl">
            AMSOIL guidance, maintenance insights, and product education.
          </h1>

          <p class="mt-6 max-w-3xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-200">
            Explore helpful articles designed to make it easier to choose the right AMSOIL products
            and understand maintenance topics with more confidence.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="bg-white">
      <div class="mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-16 md:px-10">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
         
        </div>

        <div class="mt-10 grid gap-6 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-3">
          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
           <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.18em] text-red-700">
            Product Guides
          </p>
          <h3 class="mt-3 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
            Synthetic vs Conventional Oil: Which One Is Better?
          </h3>
          <p class="mt-3 text-base leading-7 text-slate-600">
            Learn the real differences between synthetic and conventional oil, common myths,
            and how to choose the right option for your vehicle.
          </p>
          <a
            href="/articles/synthetic-vs-conventional-oil/"
            class="mt-5 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-red-700 transition hover:text-red-800"
          >
            Read article →
          </a>

          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#005baa]">
              Oil Guidance
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
              What Type of Oil Is Best for My Car?
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-600">
              If you’ve ever stood in front of a shelf of oil bottles and felt lost, you’re not alone. The good news: you don't have to become a mechanic to choose the right oil.
            </p>
            <a
              href="/articles/what-type-of-oil-is-best-for-my-car/"
              class="mt-6 inline-flex text-sm font-bold text-[#ef1c25] transition hover:underline"
            >
              Read article
            </a>
          </article>

          <article class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-8 shadow-sm transition hover:-translate-y-1 hover:shadow-lg">
            <p class="text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[#005baa]">
              Preferred Customer
            </p>
            <h3 class="mt-4 text-2xl font-black text-slate-900">
              When the Preferred Customer option makes sense
            </h3>
            <p class="mt-4 leading-8 text-slate-600">
              See when the Preferred Customer program may be useful for repeat buyers who want ongoing savings.
            </p>
            <a
              href="https://www.amsoil.com/offers/pc/?zo=5039461"
              target="_blank"
              rel="noopener noreferrer"
              class="mt-6 inline-flex text-sm font-bold text-[#ef1c25] transition hover:underline"
            >
              Learn more
            </a>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="relative overflow-hidden bg-slate-950">
      <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-slate-950/80"></div>

      <div class="relative mx-auto max-w-7xl px-6 py-14 md:px-10 md:py-16">
        <div class="max-w-3xl">
          <p class="mb-4 text-sm font-bold uppercase tracking-[0.24em] text-cyan-300">
            Need Help Now?
          </p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl font-black text-white md:text-5xl">
            Looking for product guidance right away?
          </h2>
          <p class="mt-5 max-w-2xl text-lg leading-8 text-slate-200">
            Go straight to the ordering page or get in touch if you want help narrowing down the right AMSOIL product.
          </p>

          <div class="mt-8 flex flex-col gap-4 sm:flex-row">
            <a
              href="/how-to-order"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl bg-[#ef1c25] px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-[#d8151d]"
            >
              How to Order
            </a>

            <a
              href="/contact"
              class="inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-xl border border-white/20 px-8 py-4 text-base font-bold text-white transition hover:bg-white/10"
            >
              Contact Us
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</Layout>